  <description><![CDATA[<p>Located in the heart of fashionable St. Moritz, Hotel Hauser's has been family-run by the Hauser family for over 60 years.  The interior is a mix of the modern and traditional giving it a cosy feel. All of the rooms have been recently renovated. The owners also run a world-famous confectionary shop and restaurant just below the hotel and where half board is served, so you'll be tempted by sweet treats throughout your stay.  Or just relax on the sun terrace. </p>]]></description>
